quran[16]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,142,"Basi ni chammisile chinsomba aku juli jwagambidwa."
  37,143,"Basi ingaŵa kuti jwalakwe jwaliji mwa akunswejesya (Allah)."
  37,144,"Chisimu jungatemi m’matumbo mwakwe kwikanila lisiku lyakuwukulidwa (ŵandu m’malembe)."
  40,85,"Basi nganichiŵa chanti nikwakamuchisya chikulupi chao ndema ja ŵaiweni ipotesi Yetu. (Aji ni) nyendele ja Allah jajapite pa achikapolo Ŵakwe (janti naga ayikene mwa kuiona ipotesi toba jao nganijipocheledwaga). Ni ŵapelelwaga jele ndemajo achimakafili."
  42,49,"Uŵele wakwe Allah uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka. Jukasagumba yajukusaka. Akumpaga jwansachile ŵanache ŵachikongwe, ni akumpaga jwansachile ŵanache ŵachilume."
  42,50,"Kapena kwawanganya ŵanache ŵachilume ni ŵachikongwe (kwa mundu jumo), ni akuntendaga jwansachile kuŵa jwangaŵeleka. Chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwakombola kusyene."
  42,51,"Soni nganiyiŵa kwa mundu yanti ni kum’bechetekasya jwalakwejo Allah, ikaŵeje ni maloŵe gakuuwulidwa (mu ntima mwakwe), kapena kusyeto kwa chakusiŵilila (gambaga kupikana maloŵe ga Allah mwangali kum’bona), kapena kuntumisya Ntenga (Jibulilu) basi ni kun’juwulila yaakuisaka (Allah) kwa lisosa Lyakwe. Chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwapenani kusyene, Jwalunda lwakusokoka."
  43,31,"Ni ŵatite: “Ligongo chichi ngatulusyidwa aji Qur’an kwa mundu jwankulungwa jwa m’misi jiŵili (Maaka kapena Twaif)?”"
  43,32,"Ana ŵanganyao ni ŵaakugaŵanya ukoto wa Ambuje ŵenu? Uwwe tugaŵenye sikati jao yakulamila yao pa umi wa duniya, ni twanyakwile ŵane mwa jamanjao mauchimbichimbi pachanya pa ŵane, kuti ŵane mwa jamanjao ŵatende ŵane kuŵa ŵamasengo ŵao. Sano ukoto wa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah jajili Mbepo) niwauli wambone nnope kupunda ya (duniya) yaakusonganganya."
  43,33,"Soni ingaŵaga kuti ŵandu mpaka aŵe nkutula umpepe (wachikafili), ŵandu ŵaakunkaana (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji tungaŵichile misakasa ja silifa ja majumba gao, kwisa soni makwelelo gaakasakwelelaga (nombe nago kuŵa gasilifa)."
  44,16,"(Mwakumbusyani) lisiku lyatuchikwembekanya kwembekanya kwekulungwa (pakupeleka ipotesi kwa achimakafili), chisimu Uwwe ni ŵakuusya mbusyo (syakupoteka kusyene)."
  44,17,"Soni chisimu chene nkanayiche ŵanganyao (Makuraishi) twalinjile mayeso ŵandu ŵa Firiauna, ni jwaichilile Ntenga jwakuchimbichika (Musa)."
  44,18,"(Ni jwatite): “Mumbani achikapolo ŵa Allah (ŵanache ŵa Israila), chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”"
  45,7,"Ipotesi niyakwe jwalijose jwakulukanya unami nnope, jwasambi syejinji."
  45,8,"Jwaakupikanaga ma Ȃya ga Allah gali nkusoomedwa kukwakwe, kaneka ni jukanganichilaga (kupanganya yakanyisyidwa) mwakulikwesya nti chisawu nganijugapikana (ma Ȃyago), basi mumpani abali ja ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope."
  45,9,"Soni naga ali achimanyi chindu chinechakwe chakuumila m’ma Ȃya Getu, akasachitendelaga chipongwe, ŵanganyao akwete kupata ilagasyo yakwalusya."